# Roll a Dice LET´S ROLL

This project allows users to roll a specified number of dice and displays both the numeric results and corresponding dice images.

## HOW TO PLAY

1.select a number of dice (1-6)
2.click a ROLL button
3.Numbers will be randomly generated for each dice, and the results along with corresponding dice images will be displayed.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript 

## Features

- Generates random numbers between 1 and 6 based on the selected number of dice.
- Displays dice images corresponding to the rolled numbers.
- Responsive design that adjusts for different screen sizes.

